de.adorsys.datasafe.types.api.context.overrides

Interface OverridesRegistry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseOverridesRegistry

    public interface OverridesRegistry
    This is runtime functionality override registry (similar to Spring context). Its purpose is to provide capability to override Datasafe-classes without recompilation of Datasafe module, so purely importing Datasafe as a jar. However, one should understand that dependency graph is static, managed by Dagger library, so while it is possible to override class functionality, it is not possible to add extra dependencies.
